		</ul>

		<p>The application process for a student visa carries a higher fee if you apply from outside the UK (£335 per an applicant). Make sure to apply 3 months before your study courses start. Note that it may happen that the Immigration regulator may arrange an interview with you to know if you’re a genuine student, although your application up to that step has been alright.</p>

